---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
seoTitle: Blog | YoYo Sitar
description: Notes, stories, and updates from YoYo Sitar.
permalink: /blog/index.html
bodyClass: blog-index
---
<section class="blog-listing">
  <div class="blog-listing-head">
    <p class="blog-kicker">Journal</p>
    <h1>Stories, process, and new music updates.</h1>
    <p class="blog-intro">
      A place for release notes, reflections from the road, and behind-the-scenes writing from YoYo Sitar.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% if collections.blog.length %}
    <div class="blog-card-grid">
      {% for post in collections.blog %}
        <article class="blog-card">
          <p class="blog-card-date">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </p>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <a class="blog-card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">Read entry</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <article class="blog-card blog-card-empty">
      <h2>First post coming soon</h2>
      <p>The blog is set up and ready. New writing will appear here as soon as it is published from the CMS.</p>
    </article>
  {% endif %}
</section>
